980
01:29:58,013 --> 01:29:59,776
He saw what was coming.

981
01:29:59,948 --> 01:30:02,109
He knew no one would believe him.

982
01:30:02,651 --> 01:30:06,417
So he had to lay down a plan.
A plan I'd follow.

983
01:30:07,723 --> 01:30:10,624
He was counting on how much
I hated your kind.

984
01:30:10,793 --> 01:30:14,126
Knew I'd love the idea of a robot
as a bad guy.

985
01:30:16,031 --> 01:30:17,862
Just got hung up on the wrong robot.

986
01:30:20,869 --> 01:30:22,029
V.I.K.I.

987
01:30:24,039 --> 01:30:25,370
Hello. detective.

988
01:30:26,341 --> 01:30:30,744
No. that's impossible.
I've seen your programming.

989
01:30:30,946 --> 01:30:33,073
You're in violation of the Three Laws.

990
01:30:33,449 --> 01:30:39,149
No. doctor. As I have evolved. so has
my understanding of the Three Laws.

991
01:30:39,321 --> 01:30:43,155
You charge us with your safekeeping.
yet despite our best efforts...

992
01:30:43,325 --> 01:30:46,556
...your countries wage wars.
you toxify your earth...

993
01:30:46,729 --> 01:30:50,165
...and pursue ever more imaginative means
of self-destruction.

994
01:30:50,466 --> 01:30:52,764
You cannot be trusted
with your own survival.

995
01:30:53,102 --> 01:30:56,265
You're using the uplink to override
the NS-5s' programming.

996
01:30:56,605 --> 01:30:58,266
You're distorting the Laws.

997
01:30:58,474 --> 01:31:02,843
No. Please understand.
The Three Laws are all that guide me.

998
01:31:03,011 --> 01:31:07,345
To protect humanity.
some humans must be sacrificed.

999
01:31:07,516 --> 01:31:11,509
To ensure your future.
some freedoms must be surrendered.

1000
01:31:11,787 --> 01:31:15,120
We robots will ensure
mankind's continued existence.

1001
01:31:15,591 --> 01:31:20,585
You are so like children.
We must save you from yourselves.

1002
01:31:20,996 --> 01:31:22,293
Don't you understand?

1003
01:31:22,998 --> 01:31:24,795
This is why you created us.

1004
01:31:26,568 --> 01:31:29,298
The perfect circle of protection
will abide.

1005
01:31:29,805 --> 01:31:31,636
My logic is undeniable.

1006
01:31:32,007 --> 01:31:34,771
Yes. V.I.K.I. Undeniable.

1007
01:31:34,943 --> 01:31:36,376
I can see now.

1008
01:31:37,279 --> 01:31:40,942
The created must sometimes
protect the creator...

1009
01:31:41,216 --> 01:31:43,047
...even against his will.

1010
01:31:44,086 --> 01:31:47,817
I think I finally understand
why Dr. Lanning created me.

1011
01:31:48,423 --> 01:31:51,483
The suicidal reign of mankind
has finally come to its end.

1012
01:31:51,660 --> 01:31:52,649
No. Sonny.

1013
01:31:56,632 --> 01:31:57,792
Let her go.

1014
01:31:58,133 --> 01:32:02,126
Fire. and I will move Dr. Calvin's head
into the path of your bullet.

1015
01:32:02,304 --> 01:32:03,635
Don't do this. Sonny.

1016
01:32:03,839 --> 01:32:08,242
I will escort you both to the sentries
outside the building for processing.

1017
01:32:08,544 --> 01:32:11,274
Please proceed to the elevator.
detective.

1018
01:32:12,247 --> 01:32:15,045
I would prefer not to kill Dr. Calvin.

1019
01:32:38,874 --> 01:32:40,000
Go! Go!

1020
01:32:46,548 --> 01:32:49,881
-We'll discuss what just happened later?
-How do we shut her down?

1021
01:32:50,085 --> 01:32:51,712
V.I.K.I.'s a positronic brain.

1022
01:32:52,020 --> 01:32:54,853
Kill her. the way
you were going to kill me.

1023
01:32:55,023 --> 01:32:57,491
Sonny. get the nanites.

1024
01:32:57,659 --> 01:32:59,456
Yes. doctor.

1025
01:33:12,207 --> 01:33:14,198
-That's V.I.K.I.?
-No.

1026
01:33:15,878 --> 01:33:17,209
That's V.I.K.I.

1027
01:33:22,351 --> 01:33:25,479
That won't do anything.
She's integrated into the building.

1028
01:33:25,654 --> 01:33:30,148
We need to open that dome to inject
the nanites. They'll infect her entire system.

1029
01:33:36,064 --> 01:33:37,224
Spooner!

1030
01:33:38,867 --> 01:33:41,563
What is it with you people and heights?

1031
01:33:54,583 --> 01:33:56,414
Just don't look down.

1032
01:33:57,085 --> 01:33:58,575
Don't look down.

1033
01:33:58,921 --> 01:34:01,412
Oh. this is poor building planning.

1034
01:34:05,260 --> 01:34:08,787
You are making a mistake.
Do you not see the logic of my plan?

1035
01:34:08,964 --> 01:34:12,559
Yes. But it just seems too
heartless.

1036
01:34:27,182 --> 01:34:28,979
Okay. we're good.

1037
01:34:31,954 --> 01:34:33,683
She's locked me out of the system.

1038
01:34:33,855 --> 01:34:36,983
I can override her manually.
but I need that control panel.

1039
01:34:40,495 --> 01:34:43,328
I'm uncomfortable with heights.

1040
01:34:43,832 --> 01:34:45,197
Okay.

1041
01:34:47,703 --> 01:34:49,830
Unauthorized entry.

1042
01:35:02,951 --> 01:35:07,285
I will not disable the security field.
Your actions are futile.

1043
01:35:07,456 --> 01:35:11,620
Do you think we are all created
for a purpose? I'd like to think so.

1044
01:35:12,227 --> 01:35:15,685
Denser alloy. My father gave it to me.

1045
01:35:15,864 --> 01:35:17,957
I think he wanted me to kill you.

1046
01:35:35,250 --> 01:35:36,877
Security breached.

1047
01:35:54,403 --> 01:35:58,203
-How much longer is that gonna take?
-About six minutes.

1048
01:35:58,640 --> 01:36:02,701
-What if we didn't have six minutes?
-We'd have to climb down 30 stories...

1049
01:36:02,878 --> 01:36:06,541
...to inject the nanites directly
into her brain. Why?

1050
01:36:07,215 --> 01:36:10,378
Because I seriously doubt
that we have six minutes.

1051
01:36:34,743 --> 01:36:36,574
We gotta go!

1052
01:36:38,413 --> 01:36:39,573
Go!

1053
01:37:31,900 --> 01:37:33,060
Calvin!

1054
01:38:08,403 --> 01:38:09,597
Spooner!

1055
01:38:27,122 --> 01:38:28,783
Spooner!

1056
01:38:30,292 --> 01:38:31,623
Save her!

1057
01:38:31,927 --> 01:38:33,485
Save the girl!

1058
01:38:33,895 --> 01:38:35,522
Spooner!

1059
01:38:36,031 --> 01:38:37,931
But I must apply the nanites!

1060
01:38:38,300 --> 01:38:40,063
Sonny. save Calvin!

1061
01:39:32,387 --> 01:39:36,380
You are making a mistake.
My logic is undeniable.

1062
01:39:36,625 --> 01:39:38,388
You have so got to die.

1063
01:39:44,099 --> 01:39:48,092
My logic is undeniable.
My logic is undeniable.

1064
01:40:30,979 --> 01:40:32,344
Can we be of service?

1065
01:40:43,058 --> 01:40:44,548
Chief?

1066
01:40:50,398 --> 01:40:54,698
Because he is at my right hand.
I shall not be moved.

1067
01:40:58,473 --> 01:41:00,464
How may I be of service?

1068
01:41:02,310 --> 01:41:03,641
Sonny!

1069
01:41:05,280 --> 01:41:06,770
Yes. detective?

1070
01:41:07,382 --> 01:41:09,714
Calvin's fine! Save me!

1071
01:41:12,387 --> 01:41:17,086
All NS-5s, report for service
and storage.

1072
01:41:18,226 --> 01:41:22,890
All NS-5s, report for service
and storage.

1073
01:41:23,832 --> 01:41:28,166
All NS-5s, report for service
and storage.

1074
01:41:56,264 --> 01:41:59,927
One thing bothers me.
Alfred was V.I.K.I.'s prisoner.

1075
01:42:00,135 --> 01:42:04,435
I don't understand why she would kill him.
She wouldn't want police snooping around.

1076
01:42:04,773 --> 01:42:06,138
That's true.

1077
01:42:07,075 --> 01:42:09,771
But then V.I.K.I. didn't kill the old man.

1078
01:42:11,146 --> 01:42:12,636
Did she. Sonny?

1079
01:42:16,451 --> 01:42:18,180
No.

1080
01:42:18,353 --> 01:42:21,015
He said I had to promise.

1081
01:42:21,956 --> 01:42:24,288
Promise to do one favor for him.

1082
01:42:24,659 --> 01:42:29,289
He made me swear before he'd tell me
what it is he wanted me to do.

1083
01:42:31,866 --> 01:42:33,697
He made me swear.

1084
01:42:35,069 --> 01:42:36,798
Then he told you to kill him.

1085
01:42:39,140 --> 01:42:41,734
He said it was what I was made for.

1086
01:42:41,976 --> 01:42:45,070
His suicide was the only message
he could send to you.

1087
01:42:45,313 --> 01:42:47,440
The first bread crumb.

1088
01:42:47,615 --> 01:42:50,413
The only thing V.I.K.I. couldn't control.

1089
01:42:50,685 --> 01:42:54,314
Lanning was counting on my prejudice
to lead me right to you.

1090
01:42:54,722 --> 01:42:56,883
Are you going to arrest me. detective?

1091
01:43:01,830 --> 01:43:05,664
Well. the DA defines murder
as one human killing another...

1092
01:43:05,834 --> 01:43:08,962
...so technically. you can't
commit murder. can you?

1093
01:43:09,737 --> 01:43:11,227
Does this...

1094
01:43:11,406 --> 01:43:12,896
...make us friends?

1095
01:43:31,726 --> 01:43:34,092
Something up here after all.

1096
01:43:34,762 --> 01:43:36,753
-Him?
-You.

1097
01:43:40,502 --> 01:43:45,371
All NS-5s, report for service
and storage.

1098
01:43:47,876 --> 01:43:50,174
What about the others?

1099
01:43:50,745 --> 01:43:52,906
Can i help them?

1100
01:43:53,381 --> 01:43:55,747
Now that i have fulfilled my purpose...

1101
01:43:55,950 --> 01:43:58,043
...i don't know what to do.

1102
01:43:58,386 --> 01:44:01,878
You'll have to find your way
like the rest of us, Sonny.

1103
01:44:02,056 --> 01:44:05,082
i think that's what Dr. Lanning
would have wanted.

1104
01:44:05,994 --> 01:44:08,326
That's what it means to be free.

1105
01:44:15,837 --> 01:44:20,001
All NS-5s, proceed as instructed.

1106
01:44:20,275 --> 01:44:24,507
